  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/e33ec58f6de8773ab04e3b227bf7541f.webp?t=1645811895\" width=328 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/a748bf427212492c18646bf4aa5b3119.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=520 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/a748bf427212492c18646bf4aa5b3119.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/a748bf427212492c18646bf4aa5b3119.mp4?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> You are Jenny Hopkins a brilliant archaeologist on a magical and perilous adventure to discover the dark secrets of Egypt’s past and banish the long forgotten evil from this world forever.<br> Your fiancé William finds a strange ancient artifact with old writings on it in Egypt. You manage to translate it and travel to Egypt.<br>Only to find the city of Alexandria plagued with monsters and William very sick. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/209c8383dcf76780418757318634f6ae.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=520 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/209c8383dcf76780418757318634f6ae.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/209c8383dcf76780418757318634f6ae.mp4?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> Embark on an epic Egyptian journey to find out who's behind all of this.  Make new friends along the way. Discover magical artifacts.<br>Complete non-repetitive puzzles, mini-games and HO levels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/da3a5fc08e32d454d3bc5f2e27728001.avif?t=1645811895\" width=338 height=80 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore 3 Ancient Realms + Bonus Chapter<br></li><li>More than 5 hours of Gameplay !<br></li><li>Over 80 locations<br></li><li>Collect Arcana coins to build your own Palace. Choose Medieval, Arabic, Renaissance or mix them all!<br></li><li>32 Mini and Hidden Object games<br></li><li>40 Morph Objects<br></li><li>Unlock 15 Achievements<br></li><li>Hire Companions to help you with your quests <br></li><li>Interactive animated characters with voiceovers<br></li><li>Incredible music and sound effects<br></li><li>Hint system to help you through your adventure, Casual and Normal mode</li></ul>Take a look at some Steam Achievements !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/46b092018df50b9fd1f2459735ebbbbc.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=224 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/46b092018df50b9fd1f2459735ebbbbc.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/46b092018df50b9fd1f2459735ebbbbc.mp4?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/e8489f39b34b07b5e7f3b89c69605b18.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=224 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/e8489f39b34b07b5e7f3b89c69605b18.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/e8489f39b34b07b5e7f3b89c69605b18.mp4?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/3dac9ae6f0abf4fda28e5051d9fcdf21.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=224 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/3dac9ae6f0abf4fda28e5051d9fcdf21.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/3dac9ae6f0abf4fda28e5051d9fcdf21.mp4?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/9603c316c28c457b9877a34e691b3df8.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=224 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/9603c316c28c457b9877a34e691b3df8.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/9603c316c28c457b9877a34e691b3df8.mp4?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/ae8fe8e117ec94cce41dce46d0e09f95.poster.avif?t=1645811895\" width=520 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431270/extras/ae8fe8e117ec94cce41dce46d0e09f95.webm?t=1645811895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea